<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span><span class="c5">طالب:</span>. . . . . . . . .<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>لا المفترض تربطه مع القدم.<a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
